videos.description: Virginia Tech's Devin Wilson sneaks through the paint and gets the ball from Chris Clarke for the open lay-in.
videos.headline: Wilson fake screen leads him to the basket

videos.description: Justin Robinson fights for the loose ball and looks up the court to Tyrie Jackson for the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: VT's stellar defense leads to a free slam

videos.description: TJ Gibbs drains half-court shot at the buzzer to give the Fighting Irish momentum going into halftime.
videos.headline: Gibbs sinks buzzer-beater from half court

videos.description: Justin Bibbs drives through the paint and is rejected by Nikola Djogo.
videos.headline: Djogo denies Bibbs

videos.description: Justin Robinson takes the ball right out of TJ Gibbs' hands and lobs it down the court for a Chris Clarke slam.
videos.headline: Clarke seals the deal for the Hokies
